dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2015.[This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained predominantly by conducting field work using GPS technology. Features contained in the data set include all road centerlines countywide and associated attributes and annotation. The Lincoln County Land Information Office plans to maintain this digital data in geodatabase format in an ESRI ArcSDE environment using ArcMap tools.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
